20 calculate the amount of the tax credit under this section equal to a percentage of the amount
21 of property tax imposed on the eligible assessment of the qualified property as follows:
22 (i) 80% in each of the 1st 8 taxable years following the calendar year
23 in which the property initially becomes a qualified property;
24 (ii) 70% in the 9th taxable year;
25 (iii) 60% in the 10th taxable year;
26 (iv) 50% in the 11th taxable year;
27 (v) 40% in the 12th taxable year; and
28 (vi) 30% in the 13th taxable year.

